videos.description: In their first game since Tyler Trent lost his battle with bone cancer, the Purdue basketball team honors his legacy with specially designed warm-up shirts.
videos.headline: Boilermakers honor Tyler Trent with warm-up shirts

videos.description: Tyler Cook drives baseline and elevates for a thunderous two-handed slam on Aaron Wheeler, cutting the Purdue lead to 15-14.
videos.headline: Cook jams all over Wheeler

videos.description: Sasha Stefanovic steps in front of Ryan Kriener's pass, then finds Nojel Eastern under the rim for a huge one-handed flush.
videos.headline: Stefanovic steals, Eastern slams
